{"TopicId":173389,"ForumId":98,"TopicTitle":"Research Flat Earth - \u0022Mad\u0022 Mike flight [WIP Update 1]","CreatedByName":"PietrOZ","CreatedById":149891,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-02T16:27:55Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"PietrOZ","CreatedById":149891,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-02T16:27:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EDownload here --\u0026gt;\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbal.curseforge.com/projects/research-flat-earth-mad-mike-flight/files\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://kerbal.curseforge.com/projects/research-flat-earth-mad-mike-flight/files\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn an effort to finally understand if the earth is a globe or not, Mike built his steam powered rocket and launched it in the Mojave Desert on March 25, 2018.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRecreate Mike\u0027s mission by launching a small rocket from the back of a truck in the middle of the desert, and landing it 400m away after having reached an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Apoapsis\u0022\u003EAp\u003C/abbr\u003E of 550m.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00220wBNYoM.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/0wBNYoM.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022Mad\u0022 Mike Hughes climbing into the rocket.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022rGGUm43.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/rGGUm43.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe steam powerd rocket lifts off.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022mKpApIM.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/mKpApIM.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe rocket soon after landing in the Mojave Desert.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EDownload here --\u0026gt;\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbal.curseforge.com/projects/research-flat-earth-mad-mike-flight/files\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://kerbal.curseforge.com/projects/research-flat-earth-mad-mike-flight/files\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-04-03T22:27:57Z\u0022 title=\u002204/03/2018 10:27  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EApril 3, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by PietrOZ\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Eupdate point system, better directions\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dimas152","CreatedById":179714,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-04T08:24:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwhy don\u0027t u use these smol SRBs instead?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PietrOZ","CreatedById":149891,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-04T16:15:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223344491\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022173389\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221522830251\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022[INDO]dimas_1502\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, [INDO]dimas_1502 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwhy don\u0027t u use these smol SRBs instead?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe real rocket was steam powered, not solid, to me it is better resembled by a liquid fuel engine...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt also made it look more like the real thing \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022